=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Sandra Gomes","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_546307","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=37872628&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Sandra Gomes","ctime_ts":1304854732,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/110350778/37872656","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?replyto=13407821","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13407821#t13407821","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13407821#t13407821","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13407821#t13407821","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_546310","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://www.facebook.com/juliana.sane","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":13407821,"talkid":52374,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13407821#t13407821","upictitle":"Juliana Sane: pic#110350778","article":"I'm pretty sure you have many fans in Brazil. I for one am trying to get everyone addicted to the series. Me and my colleagues talk about the books every day at the office. We can't wait to read a Dance with Dragons. The series starts today on Brazil, I was just watching the making of with my father. The thing is it's not that hard to get everyone to like, it's such a great story :) Congratulations! You're the best :)","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"6 years ago","ctime":"May 8 2011, 11:42:00 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Brasil","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/juliana.sane","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?