br />That's the best news in a long time.<br />I've missed the last time you were here in Portugal, and have felt really bad since it's one of those once in a lifetime chances (or so i thought) to meet your favorite author.<br />I'll be sure to take all my Dreamsongs and Comic adaptation books for signing too!! :D<br />I wonder if you also sign the Game of Thrones board game, or if that would be a bit too much...<br /><br />Miguel","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"6 years ago","ctime":"May 13 2011, 13:38:18 UTC","parent":13411917,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100000286910220","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Miguel Sk","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_554218","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=37973726&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Miguel Sk","ctime_ts":1305293898,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/110360838/37880850","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?replyto=13414989","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13414989#t13414989","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13414989#t13414989","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13414989#t13414989","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_547019","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://www.facebook.com/juliana.ncorrea","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":13414989,"talkid":52402,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13414989#t13414989","upictitle":"Juliana Correa: pic#110360838","article":"Mr. Martin, your fans in Brazil probably outnumber your portuguese fans, by now... everyday there are more of us, and if you consider the country dimensions...lol!!!! Unfortunately we're still waiting for the third book, which is a privilege only our friends from portugal have, what a pitty! <br /><br />That's my first comment here, so let me end up by saying that me and my gradma are big fans! She doesn't speak English at all and she'll be happy to read the interview!<br /><br /><br />","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"6 years ago","ctime":"May 8 2011, 23:22:17 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"OBRIGADO!","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/juliana.ncorrea","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Juliana Correa","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_547019","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=37880850&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Juliana Correa","ctime_ts":1304896937,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?replyto=13417293","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13417293#t13417293","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13417293#t13417293","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13417293#t13417293","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"fuintur","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://fuintur.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":13417293,"talkid":52411,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=1341