":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_551391","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=37940280&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Eurico Pinto da Costa","ctime_ts":1305156164,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?replyto=13684301","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13684301#t13684301","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13684301#t13684301","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13684301#t13684301","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"persius83","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://persius83.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":13684301,"talkid":53454,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/214093.html?thread=13684301#t13684301","upictitle":"persius83: pic#0","article":"That will be just great! You surely have plenty of fans in Portugal (and in our brother-country Brazil as well, i'm sure :p). Within my group of friends there's at least 8 people reading the Song of Ice and Fire Saga and every single one of them is just having a blast! Everyday when i travel by subway in Lisbon, and in many other places, i see more and more people reading your books, it seems they're getting quite popular. Your work is just of the best caliber though, so that's nothing to be amazed at :)<br /><br />As an avid reader of good books in general, and fantasy fiction in particular, I could never thank you enough, but in just a  few words, thank you a lot for your amazing work, Mr Martin! Please keep it up! <br /><br />Obrigado, and hope you enjoy your visit when you come to Portugal!","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"5 years ago","ctime":"May 25 2011, 17:08